high_descs: Turn right and go to the front of the counter on the left of the sink.
Pick up the gray spoon on the counter.
Move over left to the cabinet below the counter with a gray plate on top.
Place the spoon inside the gray pot in the cabinet.
Pick up the pot with the spoon in it.
Move over right to the sink.
Place the pot with the spoon in it into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move the pot with a spoon in it to the sink.

high_descs: Turn right then left towards the stove, then right towards the sink.
From the sink pick up the spoon in between two spatulas.
Turn left then head towards the stove, turn right then face the counter top
Open the cabinet door underneath the counter top then place the spoon inside the bowl.
Remove the pan from the cabinet then close the door.
Turn right then head towards the sink.
Place the bowl in the sink on the right side.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a spoon inside the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, hang a left around the counter and walk to the sink on the right.
Pick up the spoon from the left side of the sink.
Turn left and hang a right at the stove to face the counter.
Open the lower cabinet under the counter and put the spoon inside the bowl.
Pick up the bowl with the spoon from inside the cabinet and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the bowl with the spoon inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a spoon in a sink.
